<seg id="572">Essential Examination Results</seg>
<seg id="573">BRH</seg>
<seg id="574">Multi-Eye Principle</seg>
<seg id="575">The audited awarding authorities implemented the specifications for the multi-eye principle at the opening dates.</seg>
