<seg id="588">Summary Findings</seg>
<seg id="589">The regulations of both countries for the opening of the offers agree in relevant parts. They take into account both the multi-eye principle and the principle of transparency. As a result, the risks of corruption and manipulation can be significantly limited when the offers are opened.</seg>
