<seg id="597">Requirements of EU law and Prevention of corruption</seg>
<seg id="598">The requirements of the EU provide for a multi-stage procedure:</seg>
<seg id="599">The suitability of the bidders must first be determined.</seg>
<seg id="600">Bidders must be economically and financially efficient and have the necessary professional and technical expertise.</seg>
