<seg id="710">The companies have the possibility to examine the intended award by electronic means or by fax within 10 days or, in the case of other means of communication, within 15 days and, if necessary, to initiate a review procedure.</seg>
<seg id="711">A contract may not be concluded before the expiry of this information period.</seg>
