<seg id="613">On the basis of the information in USt pre-registrations or ust declarations as well as audit instructions, qualified auditors select the cases to be examined and ensure the correct taxation.</seg>
<seg id="614">Appropriate management processes and risk management systems should be introduced to reduce revenue shortfalls at VAT and at the same time increase the risk of discovery for unreliable entrepreneurs.</seg>
